I found a duplicates of this bug (1915, 1674), but they were closed in the 
RESOLVED FIXED state, even if the problem still persist. I use the 1.4.4 
version, and still the importNode() method deletes attributes from the 
document. Since I don't know any workarounds, this one is very important to me. 
